---
title: Creamy Prawn & Bacon Spaghetti with Garlic and Green Chilli
description: Long day? Too tired to cook? We know the feeling...With just 15 minutes hands on cooking time, this deliciously simple dish is the perfect thing to knock together if you’re in a hurry to get dinner on the table. Packed with juicy prawns and crispy pancetta, this velvety creamy spaghetti is the thing pasta dreams are made of! Buon appetito!
